channel.title: RSPS Control Panel v1.1: Compiler, Restarter, and Editor
channel.description:
Was bored so I felt like making this.
Image(s): [IMG]http://i198.photobucket.com/albums/aa304/Rush_Hour_3/rspscp.png[/img] [IMG]http://i198.photobucket.com/albums/aa304/Rush_Hour_3/rspscptools.png[/img]
Download(s): [url=http://www.mediafire.com/?nlj24ddwn1o]http://www.mediafire.com/?nlj24ddwn1o[/url]
Features:
[ul][*]Compiler [*]Great server restarter [*]Server editor [*]If the server crashes then it is automatically restarted [*]No server editing required [*]Syntax highlighting [*]One touch client opening [*]Setting saving [*]More to come![/ul]

item.dc:creator: @UberMegaFly UberMegaFly
item.description:
@UberMegaFly wrote:

[quote=“Lin, post:24, topic:278088”][quote author=UberMegaFly link=topic=367062.msg2801900#msg2801900 date=1243482864]

Looks beyond great. However, I disbelieve you made this. Why? This was your first post here. Not saying it isn’t, but yea…

My name is Supah Fly, i am admin on fagex.net (supahfly@fagex.net) go ahead and add me if you dont believe me… im a c#, php, vb, js, asp, kind of person. anyone who knows me knows that my runescape username was ubermegafly… -.- it was even on my blog

whoever thinks its a virus is a complete fucktard, go check where the images are loading from, its just an image, not something that downloads a virus to your computer.

i could open-source this project and moparscapers will still say its a virus.

it was posted on rsever and rlocus by who other then ME, and i posted it here because it would get leeched here by some other random kid and take all my credit.

and if you think i ripped it, prove it kid, i got plenty of proof to backup that i know what im talking about and i am fully capable of adding on and recreating this in every aspect of this program.

its my first post because mods didnt allow my other guides on mysqling a server or better file handling to go through.

“He didn’t make it, it was made by a Super Moderator on RPSSP and help from RSPServer” i am the owner of rspserver (its blocked = my site wins) you dumbfuck i have the source code, i dont ever give my source away, i know how to program better then everyone on my whole site combined to the 10th power, and m a r t y (the owner of project rsps (official server for my site)) is the only exception (though hes not better then me :p)

if you really want me to prove who i am ill have like 30 people (.1/1000s of people i know) to come post here verifying who i am…

http://www.supahfly.net/pids/ if you really think im some leecher, as far as i know nobody has done this yet…
[/quote]I think we’d all just enjoy it if you got the fuck off. To think I was flaming people earlier cause I was in a pissy mood makes me wonder if I really was from reading your post (Which by the way, made you look stupid). You get worked up over the little things.

“you dumbfuck i have the source code” Ya. There’s no proof and you’re getting all worked up about not knowing someone important (Eg. you.) Gtfo.[/quote]

oh im sad now i got told off by some nobody with 200 rep

i dont give a fuck what you think i will do what i want, if i dont post it here someone else will and take my credits, forget that right now.

and at the last part there, the last little line you wrote, makes no sense whatsoever.
